                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12941325" author="gtully" created="Thu, 29 Oct 2009 17:09:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cleanup task now has fixed delay period rather than fixed rate. The cleanupPeriod is now the delay between the end of task completion and the next run. This ensures it will not hog the db.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
